{"word":"ταχύς","slug":"ταχύς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ταχύς, εῖα, ύ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ orig.\">orig.</a> unclear] ‘exhibiting swiftness’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on action, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b>quick <a href='B:660 1:19'>Js 1:19</a>;</b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> <el>ταχύ</el>, <b>quickly, in a hurry <a href='B:470 5:25'>Mt 5:25</a>; <a href='B:470 28:7'>28:7f</a>; <a href='B:490 15:22'>Lk 15:22</a>; <a href='B:500 11:29'>J 11:29</a>.</b> The use of <el>τ.</el> in Rv appears to fall in<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on time, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>within a short time, soon <a href='B:480 9:39'>Mk 9:39</a>; <a href='B:730 2:5'>Rv 2:5</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 16; <a href='B:730 3:11'>3:11</a>; <a href='B:730 11:14'>11:14</a>; <a href='B:730 22:7'>22:7</a>, <a href='B:730 22:12'>12</a>, <a href='B:730 22:20'>20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τάχος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τέ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}